      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Organizations</a> * Chemnitz University of Technology</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Chemnitz-TU-StraNa.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Chemnitz-TU-StraNa.jpg/330px-Chemnitz-TU-StraNa.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"209\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Chemnitz-TU-StraNa.jpg/500px-Chemnitz-TU-StraNa.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3a/Chemnitz-TU-StraNa.jpg/960px-Chemnitz-TU-StraNa.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Chemnitz-TU-StraNa.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>TU Chemnitz <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p><b>Chemnitz University of Technology</b>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chemnitz\">Chemnitz</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Germany\">Germany</a>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#People\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">People</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"People\">People</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chemnitz_University_of_Technology&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: People\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Werner_Dilger\">Werner Dilger</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.andreas-ittner.de/prof-dr-andreas-ittner.html\">Andreas Ittner</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Olaf_Jenkner\" title=\"Olaf Jenkner\">Olaf Jenkner</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Andreas_Junghanns\" title=\"Andreas Junghanns\">Andreas Junghanns</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Grit_Lachmann\" title=\"Grit Lachmann\">Grit Lachmann</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Christian_Posthoff\" title=\"Christian Posthoff\">Christian Posthoff</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Michael_Schlosser\" title=\"Michael Schlosser\">Michael Schlosser</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Rainer_Staudte\" title=\"Rainer Staudte\">Rainer Staudte</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bernd_Steinbach\" title=\"Bernd Steinbach\">Bernd Steinbach</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Jens_Zeidler\" title=\"Jens Zeidler\">Jens Zeidler</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chemnitz_University_of_Technology&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> Johannes Steinmüller, Holger Langner, Marc Ritter, <a href=\"/Jens_Zeidler\" title=\"Jens Zeidler\">Jens Zeidler</a> (Hrsg.): <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.qucosa.de/recherche/frontdoor/?tx_slubopus4frontend%5bid%5d=urn:nbn:de:bsz:ch1-200800898\">15 Jahre Künstliche Intelligenz an der TU Chemnitz</a>.</i> Chemnitzer Informatikberichte, April 2008, CSR-08-01</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chemnitz_University_of_Technology&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chemnitz_University_of_Technology\">Chemnitz University of Technology from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tu-chemnitz.de/en/\">Chemnitz University of Technology</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chemnitz_University_of_Technology&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">TU Chemnitz Main-building <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stra%C3%9Fe_der_Nationen\">Strasse der Nationen</a>, Image by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Kolossos\">Kolossos</a>, February 26, 2008, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chemnitz_University_of_Technology\">Chemnitz University of Technology from Wikipedia</a> </span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301132539\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.073 seconds\nReal time usage: 0